{"tid":901163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Stan Lee過世享壽95歲 漫威之父催生鋼鐵人蜘蛛人","createTime":"2018-11-13T19:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T01:57:11.000Z","uid":48210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a02b1ab69533b1490571f2f518db33f5657b92e","tid":901163,"uid":48210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T19:28:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201811130008.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201811130008.aspx&d=yHTls%2Fhbcz%2B6IRu6YooCMBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0083b98d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201811130008.aspx</a><br />\n（中央社洛杉磯12日綜合外電報導）參與創造出蜘蛛人、鋼鐵人和綠巨人浩克等漫畫英雄人物的電視名人史丹李（Stan Lee）已辭世，享壽95歲。他發想出的這些人物已成為通俗文化的傳奇，拍成了許多叫座的電影。<br />\n<br />\n身兼作家和編輯的史丹李是漫威漫畫公司（Marvel Comics）在1960年代躍登為漫畫書籍出版巨擘的關鍵人物。他與柯比（Jack Kirby）和迪特科（Steve Ditko）等畫家聯手創造出了上述漫畫英雄，令一代又一代的年輕讀者入迷。"},{"pid":"150ca06abf86c7df8c869f3a0095b3c0b2d289ba","tid":901163,"uid":48210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T20:21:21.000Z","msg":"Stan Lee R.I.P.<br />\n今年真係死好多名人"},{"pid":"ac9052c61fc435ae27b2c40c44e40311ae6b93d9","tid":901163,"uid":48210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"冇人理"},{"pid":"a2afa65cf0543b9be8b0d57e8d9527222bf42c98","tid":901163,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:57:11.000Z","msg":"劃咗幾十年仲有得劃，同日漫一樣，啲bug多到，就快一拳可以打爆地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}